{"tid":1759643,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩大家幫手荷蘭戰線！！","createTime":"2019-11-27T19:13:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T02:20:43.000Z","uid":15677,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f0d4002d9e6e20e572e23fba974ff247766e093e","tid":1759643,"uid":15677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T19:13:54.000Z","msg":"麻煩國際戰線留意下荷蘭！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然荷蘭pass咗Magnitsky Act 但係作為係荷蘭讀緊書嘅香港人 其實荷蘭都一直俾班支那學生蠶食緊！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事源係咁的 ：<br />\n<br />\nUniversity of Groningen 嘅學生報紙Ukrant 係11月18日報咗關於荷蘭交換生Nora Leidinger 係香港嘅所見所聞同佢對香港學生同抗爭者嘅支持 <br />\n<br />\n（原文：<a href=\"https://www.ukrant.nl/magazine/its-not-fair-that-i-get-to-go-home/?lang=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ukrant.nl%2Fmagazine%2Fits-not-fair-that-i-get-to-go-home%2F%3Flang%3Den&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9Der6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=8fd706ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ukrant.nl/magazine/its-not-fair-that-i-get-to-go-home/?lang=en</a>）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ETaHCu0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FETaHCu0.png&h=b102c934&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果Groningen支那學生組織ACSSG即日出聲明屌鳩Ukrant 同Nora, 又係講個啲不容許外人說三道四嘅飛機文<br />\n（佢地個所謂官網：<a href=\"http://www.acssg.nl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.acssg.nl&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9Der6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=c1e9da98\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.acssg.nl</a>）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3C4xfhc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3C4xfhc.jpg&h=b4a666cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/42W7OCd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F42W7OCd.jpg&h=155c07a1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2o7Ox3U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2o7Ox3U.jpg&h=fc60cdd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結果今日 Ukrant 出多咗篇article 話香港嘅抗爭令間大學入面嘅中國人嘅意見有分歧<br />\n（傳送門：<a href=\"https://www.ukrant.nl/magazine/worlds-apart/?lang=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ukrant.nl%2Fmagazine%2Fworlds-apart%2F%3Flang%3Den&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9Der6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=ef48a6b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ukrant.nl/magazine/worlds-apart/?lang=en</a>）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gOU9hvO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgOU9hvO.png&h=1d05abae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地訪問咗中國學生同中國staff 得一個學生撐 <br />\n訪問入面班assistant professors 藍到on 9，講埋啲廢老藍絲論 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2vgGXU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2vgGXU.png&h=df96e369&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係仲未完！<br />\n<br />\n班支那學生group話Ukrant 係fake news 仲想起支持香港嘅中國學生底 （原諒我blur名 唔想俾佢地班人知入面有我地人mon住）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wqciVic.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwqciVic.png&h=ae1870af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/28/030550_7d51b8cacfc8df19e97ff81ffc82c454.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F28%2F030550_7d51b8cacfc8df19e97ff81ffc82c454.png&h=559242da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nUkrant 而家俾班支那人spam緊，希望各位連登仔幫下佢！！ <br />\n（傳多次：<a href=\"https://www.ukrant.nl/magazine/worlds-apart/?lang=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ukrant.nl%2Fmagazine%2Fworlds-apart%2F%3Flang%3Den&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9Der6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=ef48a6b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ukrant.nl/magazine/worlds-apart/?lang=en</a>） <br />\n<br />\n係下面留言希望大家幫手 有荷蘭學生出聲 但好撚多五毛係到downvote <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係荷蘭讀書嘅香港人真心唔多 尤其係Groningen 北到唔北 <br />\n<br />\n中大理大保衛戰個幾日 我地搞咗個大學聯署 <br />\n亦已經遞咗請願信俾班university board <br />\n係荷蘭Amsterdam, Rotterdam 同The Hague 亦有不同嘅活動支持港人<br />\n<br />\n問題係間大學對香港事件冷感到仆街 （佢地之前仲想喺中國煙台起學校）<br />\n我地有人貼咗關於香港嘅海報係大學 結果即日俾人請咗去dean&rsquo;s office話政治問題唔好帶入大學 <br />\n<br />\n我地黎緊亦會send email 俾學生報記者希望佢地會訪問香港學生，希望佢地做好啲fact check先報，同埋話佢地知已經遞咗請願信， 希望可以逼到間大學正視， 唔好已讀不回我地封聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n荷蘭聽落好似冇其他國家嘅大學咁同啲支那學生有激烈衝突 其實好多時都係因為佢地好多都愛理不理 <br />\n<br />\n請大家唔好放棄荷蘭戰線！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係Ukrant 留言多謝佢地同Nora 報導香港嘅情況同埋希望佢地同時value 在荷香港人嘅意見！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5516c584ce20723f45a4b1ce2d5e510a57523294","tid":1759643,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T19:15:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6a4a0fe3b461a89e5c83300f97d138fe97d49640","tid":1759643,"uid":310759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T19:15:51.000Z","msg":"推唔到都同你推"},{"pid":"83b9bb9ba1eb9a39a20f08bee8afb06f6636677a","tid":1759643,"uid":15677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T19:15:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a4d5035c8d135c8c419354edcabceb0227f248e0","tid":1759643,"uid":266755,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T19:17:01.000Z","msg":"唔滿意覺得唔fair，咪去天安門反影囉！"},{"pid":"d6662ac4b52cbf4a1a6430d07285be7270947312","tid":1759643,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T19:17:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6e9eb345c59d644a7153ffa41c99cb59fcd14d4a","tid":1759643,"uid":15677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":